Description: Rim, handle plate, and handle sherd of East Greek grey ware column-krater; handle attached to outside, not underside, of handle-plate; dull grey fabric core with numerous mica and limestone inclusions; worn dark grey slip on handle-plate, on handle, and on exterior.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (GL.035)
